headline: 2 Profitable Stocks on Our Buy List and 1 Facing Headwinds
summary: Not all profitable companies are built to last - some rely on outdated models or unsustainable advantages. Just because a business is in the green today doesn’t mean it will thrive tomorrow.

headline: Dow Jones Futures Rise After Trump Speech; Nvidia Earnings Loom
summary: Dow Jones futures rose slightly Wednesday morning, along with S&P 500 futures and Nasdaq futures.  The stock market rebounded Tuesday after Monday's sell-off, with the Dow Jones regaining key support.  Advanced Micro Devices jumped on a big deal with Meta Platforms, with Taiwan Semiconductor and Monolithic Power also notable winners.

headline: Dow Jones Futures: Trump Gives State Of The Union Speech; Nvidia Earnings Loom
summary: Dow Jones futures edged higher overnight, along with S&P 500 futures and Nasdaq futures.  President Donald Trump is giving his State of the Union address with tariffs in flux and U.S.-Iran tensions continuing.  The stock market rebounded Tuesday after Monday's sell-off, with the Dow Jones regaining key support.
